trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialog"></xref> custom place collection for [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Representerar en post i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialog"> </xref> anpassade plats samlingen för [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The default open and save dialog boxes on [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] have an area on the left side of the dialog box titled **Favorite Links**.
trans-unit.target: Standard öppna och spara dialogrutor på [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] har ett område till vänster i dialogrutan med titeln **favoritlänkar**.

trans-unit.source: This area is called custom places.
trans-unit.target: Det här området kallas anpassade platser.

trans-unit.source: This class represents a custom place.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen representerar en anpassad plats.

trans-unit.source: On [!INCLUDE[winxp](~/add/includes/winxp-md.md)] or [!INCLUDE[winxpsvr](~/add/includes/winxpsvr-md.md)], this class does not have any effect.
trans-unit.target: På [!INCLUDE[winxp](~/add/includes/winxp-md.md)] eller [!INCLUDE[winxpsvr](~/add/includes/winxpsvr-md.md)], den här klassen har inte någon effekt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"></xref> class with a custom place identified by a [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folder GUID.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"> </xref> klass med en anpassad plats som identifieras av en [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] känd mapp-GUID.

trans-unit.source: For a list of the available [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folders, see [Known Folder GUIDs for File Dialog Custom Places](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) or the KnownFolders.h file in the [!INCLUDE[winSDK](~/add/includes/winsdk-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: En lista över de tillgängliga [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] kända mappar, se [känd mapp-GUID för filen dialogrutan Anpassade platser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) eller KnownFolders.h-filen i den [!INCLUDE[winSDK](~/add/includes/winsdk-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Guid> that represents a [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folder.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Guid>som representerar en [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] känd mapp.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: with a specified folder path to a custom place.
trans-unit.target: med en angiven sökväg till en anpassad plats.

trans-unit.source: A folder path to the custom place.
trans-unit.target: En sökväg till den anpassa platsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folder GUID for the custom place.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] känd mapp-GUID för den anpassa platsen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Guid> that indicates the [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folder for the custom place.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Guid>som anger den [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] känd mapp för den anpassa platsen.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: If the custom place was specified with a folder path, then an empty GUID is returned.
trans-unit.target: Om den anpassa platsen har angetts med en mappsökväg, returneras ett tomt GUID.

trans-unit.source: For a list of the available [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folders, see [Known Folder GUIDs for File Dialog Custom Places](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) or the KnownFolders.h file in the [!INCLUDE[winSDK](~/add/includes/winsdk-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: En lista över de tillgängliga [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] kända mappar, se [känd mapp-GUID för filen dialogrutan Anpassade platser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) eller KnownFolders.h-filen i den [!INCLUDE[winSDK](~/add/includes/winsdk-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the folder path to the custom place.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger sökvägen till den anpassade plats.

trans-unit.source: A folder path to the custom place.
trans-unit.target: En sökväg till den anpassa platsen.

trans-unit.source: If the custom place was specified with a [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] Known Folder GUID, then an empty string is returned.
trans-unit.target: Om den anpassa platsen har angetts med ett [!INCLUDE[wiprlhext](~/add/includes/wiprlhext-md.md)] känd mapp-GUID och sedan en tom sträng returneras.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that represents this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en sträng som representerar detta <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"> </xref> instans.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som representerar detta <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.FileDialogCustomPlace"> </xref> instans.
